### 7.4 Dark Mode vs Light Mode Mapping

| Screen | Mode | Rationale |
|--------|------|-----------|
| Landing page | Light (silver-gray `#F0F0F0` base) | Premium feel, from reference imgs 6/7 |
| Auth pages | Light | Clean, no distraction |
| Onboarding | Light | Approachable |
| Chat | Light (white content area) | Readability for messages |
| Chat sidebar (desktop) | Dark (`--dark-sidebar`) | Visual separation, from ref img 3 |
| Dashboard (desktop) | Dark (`--dark-bg`) | Data visibility, from ref img 4 |
| Dashboard (mobile) | Light | Readability on small screens, from ref img 9 |
| Products / Inventory / Transactions | Light | Standard CRUD, readability |
| Settings | Light | Standard forms |
| Final CTA section (landing) | Dark (`#0D0D0D`) | Dramatic contrast, from ref img 8 |

### 7.5 Framer Motion Animation Specs

```typescript
// src/lib/animations.ts

export const chatMessageAppear = {
  initial: { opacity: 0, y: 10 },
  animate: { opacity: 1, y: 0 },
  transition: { duration: 0.2, ease: 'easeOut' },
};

export const floatingStatCard = {
  animate: {
    y: [0, -8, 0],
  },
  transition: {
    duration: 3,
    repeat: Infinity,
    ease: 'easeInOut',
  },
};

export const operationTileStagger = {
  container: {
    animate: { transition: { staggerChildren: 0.05 } },
  },
  item: {
    initial: { opacity: 0, scale: 0.95 },
    animate: { opacity: 1, scale: 1 },
    transition: { duration: 0.15 },
  },
};

export const confirmationCardAppear = {
  initial: { opacity: 0, scale: 0.95 },
  animate: { opacity: 1, scale: 1 },
  transition: { duration: 0.15, ease: 'easeOut' },
};

export const sidebarSlide = {
  initial: { x: -240 },
  animate: { x: 0 },
  exit: { x: -240 },
  transition: { duration: 0.2, ease: 'easeInOut' },
};

export const fadeIn = {
  initial: { opacity: 0 },
  animate: { opacity: 1 },
  transition: { duration: 0.3 },
};
```

### 7.6 Responsive Breakpoints

```
Mobile first. Base styles = mobile (< 640px).
sm:  640px  — larger phones landscape
md:  768px  — tablets
lg:  1024px — small laptops, desktop (sidebar appears)
xl:  1280px — full desktop (context panel appears)
```

**Breakpoint behaviors:**
- `< lg`: Single column. Bottom nav visible. Sidebar hidden (slide-out drawer on menu tap). No context panel.
- `≥ lg`: Three-column. Sidebar visible (240px). Content center. No context panel unless opened.
- `≥ xl`: Three-column. Sidebar (240px). Content center. Context panel (320px) visible when relevant (product detail, transaction detail).

